{"action":"opened","issue":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/SciML/DifferentialEquations.jl/issues/956","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/SciML/DifferentialEquations.jl","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/SciML/DifferentialEquations.jl/issues/956/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/SciML/DifferentialEquations.jl/issues/956/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/SciML/DifferentialEquations.jl/issues/956/events","html_url":"https://github.com/SciML/DifferentialEquations.jl/issues/956","id":1706912491,"node_id":"I_kwDOA3ziS85lvWrr","number":956,"title":"Manual changes to precompile options in `LocalPreferences.jl` not recognized","user":{"login":"sloede","id":3637659,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM2Mzc2NTk=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3637659?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/sloede","html_url":"https://github.com/sloede","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sloede/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sloede/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sloede/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sloede/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sloede/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sloede/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sloede/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sloede/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sloede/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2023-05-12T04:39:29Z","updated_at":"2023-05-12T04:39:29Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"First of all, thanks for adding the ability to selectively [enable/disable precompilation](https://docs.sciml.ai/DiffEqDocs/stable/features/low_dep/#Controlling